    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seconds Till Destruction</strong> is a lightning-fast, randomized top-down shooter played in six-second bursts. Warp onto different floors, kill them all, then do it again! Pick up and play for instant action, or try to clear as many floors as you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/8e5a1dded89f9c10d33fc405cb50d4bf.poster.avif?t=1752865736\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/8e5a1dded89f9c10d33fc405cb50d4bf.webm?t=1752865736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/8e5a1dded89f9c10d33fc405cb50d4bf.mp4?t=1752865736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RANDOMIZED ACTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move, dash, and shoot your way through <u>50+ unique rooms</u>! Enemy spawns, room order, and weapon choices are randomized every time, so no two runs are the same!*<i><strong> </strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GUNS GALORE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield an arsenal of <u>30+ weapons</u> to use in your runs, like the reliable Auto Shotgun or the OSHA-violating Sawblade Launcher. We've got Laser Guns, Flamethrowers, and Railguns too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/5d96f970727b729de8e4ec0a130ade14.poster.avif?t=1752865736\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/5d96f970727b729de8e4ec0a130ade14.webm?t=1752865736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/5d96f970727b729de8e4ec0a130ade14.mp4?t=1752865736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SPICE IT UP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <u>15+ unique Mutators</u> to customize the game any way you like. Slow down time, go invisible, shrink your enemies, and more! Or play the <u>Mutator Roulette</u> mode for a random mutator on every floor!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO FOR THE GOLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rack up high scores to unlock new weapons and Mutators to use in your runs. If that's not enough, try going for all <u>25 achievements</u>! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BASED ON TRUE EVENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seconds Till Destruction is an accurate depiction of future events**, where a killer robot will attempt to destroy all of humanity. You have been warned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*<i>Probably. We didn't do the math.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**<i>In at least one possible timeline. No guarantees we're living in it.</i></p>",
